<h2 style="color:#5b3b33;">A Gentle Invitation to the Varsha Retreat</h2>

<p>
The Varsha Retreat is a deeply reflective space designed to explore grief,
emotional patterns, and healing through the practice of Compassionate Inquiry®.
</p>

<p>
Join us for a supportive experience where you will be gently guided to reconnect
with yourself in a safe and compassionate environment.
</p>

<p>
Many of us carry grief that has never been fully expressed or understood.
Sometimes it shows up as anxiety, exhaustion, emotional numbness, or patterns
in our relationships that we cannot seem to change.
</p>

<p>
The Varsha Retreat was created as a space where these experiences can be
approached with curiosity, compassion, and care.
Through a gentle and guided process, participants will explore the emotional
patterns and protective strategies that have shaped their lives.
</p>

<p>
When we begin to understand these patterns, something shifts.
We move from self-judgment to self-understanding — and that is where healing begins.
</p>

