<h2 style="color:#5b3b33;">What Makes This Retreat Different</h2>

<p>
Unlike many wellness retreats focused on relaxation alone,
Varsha offers a trauma-informed therapeutic approach rooted in
Compassionate Inquiry®, developed by Dr Gabor Maté.
</p>

<p>
Participants are guided through meaningful conversations and reflective
processes that support genuine emotional insight and transformation.
</p>

